"title": "3281: Holy Spirit, inspiration of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3281: holy spirit, inspiration of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit inspires prophecy and gives knowledge of God, insight and wisdom. Scripture declares itself to have been inspired by God.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit inspired the writers of Scripture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16\">2TI 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:43\">MAT 22:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:36\">MRK 12:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:16\">ACT 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:25\">ACT 4:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:25\">ACT 28:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:7\">HEB 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:8\">HEB 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:15\">HEB 10:15</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit inspires believers to honour Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:2\">1JN 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Purposes of the Holy Spirit's inspiration</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:16-2Tim3:17\">2TI 3:16–3:17</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit inspired prophecy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:2-Num24:3\">NUM 24:2–24:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:25-Num11:29\">NUM 11:25–11:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:20\">1SA 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:23\">1SA 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:18\">1CH 12:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:1\">2CH 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:14\">2CH 20:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20\">2CH 24:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">ACT 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">ACT 19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:11-1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:11–1:12</a></p>\n<h2>People aware of the Holy Spirit's inspiration</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:16\">ISA 48:16</a> <em>Isaiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a> <em>Micah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28\">ACT 15:28</a> <em>the Council of Jerusalem</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:40\">1CO 7:40</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit gives revelation</h2>\n<h3>God's purposes revealed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:10-1Cor2:13\">1CO 2:10–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:3-Eph3:6\">EPH 3:3–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:27\">1JN 2:27</a></p>\n<h3>The Messiah revealed to Simeon</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:25-Luke2:27\">LUK 2:25–2:27</a></p>\n<h3>Visions given</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28\">JOL 2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">ACT 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:10\">REV 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:2\">REV 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>Visions interpreted</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:19-Acts10:20\">ACT 10:19–10:20</a></p>\n<h3>Dreams interpreted</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38-Gen41:39\">GEN 41:38–41:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:8-Dan4:9\">DAN 4:8–4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11\">DAN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:14\">DAN 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>David's plans for the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom and knowledge are given</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:8\">1CO 12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:10\">ACT 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's fatherhood revealed to believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:15-Rom8:16\">ROM 8:15–8:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Speech is inspired by the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>Testifying to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:20\">MAT 10:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:11\">MRK 13:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:12\">LUK 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:8\">ACT 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9\">ACT 13:9</a></p>\n<h3>Instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:2\">ACT 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>Speaking in tongues</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:4\">ACT 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:44-Acts10:46\">ACT 10:44–10:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:6\">ACT 19:6</a></p>\n<h3>Prayer</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></p>",
